# Student Profile & Resume Module — Phased Implementation Plan

## Current State Summary

Your CPMS app currently has:
- **Backend**: Express + Mongoose with `User` model (fullName, email, usnNumber, password, role, department, yearOfStudy, profileComplete), JWT auth, role middleware
- **Frontend**: React + Vite + Redux Toolkit + TailwindCSS + Framer Motion, with a polished `StudentDashboard` (hero banner, stats, notices, drives, next-steps checklist), sidebar navigation with a "My Profile" link pointing to `/dashboard/student/profile` (currently renders nothing)
- **No StudentProfile model** or profile API exists yet

---

## Phase 1 — Backend: StudentProfile Model & Basic CRUD API

> **Goal**: Create the data layer and REST endpoints for student profiles.

### 1A. StudentProfile Mongoose Model

#### [NEW] [StudentProfile.model.js](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/backend/models/StudentProfile.model.js)

Create a `StudentProfile` schema linked 1:1 to `User` via `userId`:

| Field | Type | Details |
|---|---|---|
| `userId` | ObjectId (ref: User) | Required, unique, indexed |
| `phone` | String | 10-digit mobile |
| `dateOfBirth` | Date | Optional |
| `gender` | String | Enum: Male, Female, Other |
| `address` | String | Current address |
| **Academic Details** | | |
| `tenthPercentage` | Number | 0–100 |
| `tenthBoard` | String | e.g., CBSE / State Board |
| `tenthPassingYear` | Number | |
| `twelfthPercentage` | Number | 0–100 |
| `twelfthBoard` | String | |
| `twelfthPassingYear` | Number | |
| `cgpa` | Number | 0–10 scale |
| `backlogs` | Number | Active backlogs count (default: 0) |
| **Skills & Projects** | | |
| `skills` | [String] | e.g., ["React", "Node.js", "Python"] |
| `projects` | Array of `{ title, description, techStack, link }` | Max 5 projects |
| `certifications` | [String] | Optional list |
| **Resume** | | |
| `resumeUrl` | String | Cloudinary secure URL |
| `resumePublicId` | String | Cloudinary public_id (for delete/replace) |
| **Meta** | | |
| `linkedIn` | String | Optional profile URL |
| `github` | String | Optional profile URL |

- Auto-calculate and update `User.profileComplete` percentage via a pre-save hook or a utility method.

### 1B. Profile Controller & Routes

#### [NEW] [profile.controller.js](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/backend/controllers/profile.controller.js)

| Endpoint | Method | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `/api/profile/me` | GET | Student | Fetch current user's profile (auto-create empty shell if none exists) |
| `/api/profile/me` | PUT | Student | Update profile fields (partial update via `$set`) |

#### [NEW] [profile.routes.js](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/backend/routes/profile.routes.js)

Wire routes through `verifyAccessToken` + `requireRole('student')`.

#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/backend/app.js)

Register new route: `app.use('/api/profile', profileRoutes);`

### 1C. Validation

#### [NEW] [profile.validators.js](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/backend/validators/profile.validators.js)

Express-validator rules for profile update (CGPA range 0–10, percentages 0–100, phone format, URL format for LinkedIn/GitHub, etc.)

