## Phase 4 — Frontend: "My Profile" Page UI

> **Goal**: Build a premium, polished profile page matching your existing dashboard design language.

### 4A. Routing Setup

#### [MODIFY] [AppRouter.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/frontend/src/routes/AppRouter.jsx)

The current `/dashboard/student/*` wildcard route renders `StudentDashboard` for ALL sub-paths. Refactor to use nested routes:

```
/dashboard/student          → StudentDashboard (overview)
/dashboard/student/profile  → StudentProfilePage (new)
```

Use a shared `DashboardLayout` wrapper with `<Outlet />` for nested routing.

### 4B. Profile Page Component

#### [NEW] [StudentProfilePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/frontend/src/pages/dashboard/StudentProfilePage.jsx)

**Layout — 3-section card layout**:

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  PROFILE HERO (same gradient as dashboard hero)  │
│  Avatar │ Name │ Dept │ USN │ Completion Ring     │
│         │ Edit Profile / Save / Cancel buttons   │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┐
│  PERSONAL INFO      │  ACADEMIC RECORDS          │
│  ───────────────    │  ────────────────           │
│  Phone              │  10th %    │ Board  │ Year  │
│  DOB                │  12th %    │ Board  │ Year  │
│  Gender             │  CGPA      │ Backlogs      │
│  Address            │                            │
│  LinkedIn / GitHub  │                            │
└─────────────────────┴────────────────────────────┘

┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  SKILLS & PROJECTS                               │
│  ─────────────────                               │
│  [React] [Node.js] [Python]  ← Tag pills         │
│                                                  │
│  Project Cards (title, desc, stack, link)         │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  RESUME                                          │
│  ──────                                          │
│  📄 resume.pdf    [View] [Download] [Replace]    │
│  ── OR ──                                        │
│  Drag & drop upload zone (PDF only, max 2MB)     │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Two modes**:
1. **View Mode** (default) — Read-only display with clean typography, all fields shown as text
2. **Edit Mode** — Inline form fields appear (using `react-hook-form` + `zod` validation, matching your auth forms pattern)

**Design tokens** — Reuse your existing Tailwind theme: `brand-blue`, `brand-orange`, `neutral-*`, same `rounded-2xl` cards, same Framer Motion `fadeUp` animations.

### 4C. Zod Validation Schema

#### [NEW] [profileSchema.js](file:///c:/Users/Alok%20Chandra/cpms-mini-project/frontend/src/schemas/profileSchema.js)

Client-side validation matching the backend rules (CGPA 0–10, percentages 0–100, phone regex, URL patterns).

